snippet.title: Inva-taxi (pc dos)
snippet.description:
I had missed this game previously and my friend introduced it to me only a short while ago. It's some sort of cult classic. The point is to try and guess where to go by listening at the sounds these guys make. I feel like missing a chromosome myself after playing this one.

Developer: Åkesoft (1994).

More info about the game: http://www.mobygames.com/game/dos/inva-taxi

and

http://www.pouet.net/prod.php?which=28098
